            <abstract>
                <p>Relatively long magic text containing a narrative about <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8925Solomon">Solomon</persName>.
                    It contains a quotation from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur#Ps90">Ps 90:5b–6</ref>.
                    <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6337Lofgren">Oscar Anders Valfrid Löfgren</persName>, the editor of the text, equates it with the texts found in
                    <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet58">BNFet58</ref> (translated into French in 
                    <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/26XVSX24"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Basset1896Enseign"/><title level="m">Enseignements de Jésus-Christ à ses disciples et prière magique</title><title level="s">Les apocryphes éthiopiens</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">René</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Basset</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Paris</pubPlace><date>1896</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Les apocryphes éthiopiens</t:title><t:biblScope xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" unit="volume">7</t:biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">7</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">26–29</citedRange></bibl>)
                    and in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/MfVK02233">MfVK02233</ref> (edited and translated into German in
                    <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/VU8HTEQX"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Euringer1928NetzSalomons"/><title level="a">Das Netz Salomons. Ein äthiopischer Zaubertext. Nach der Hs. im ethnographischen Museum in München</title><title level="j">Zeitschrift für Semitistik und verwandte Gebiete</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Sebastian</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Euringer</t:surname></author><date>1928</date><biblScope unit="volume">6</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">76–100, 178–199, 300–314</biblScope><note type="url">http://menadoc.bibliothek.uni-halle.de/dmg/periodical/pageview/97893</note></bibl> and
                    <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/NWVX3C8Y"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Euringer1929NetzSalomons"/><title level="a">Das Netz Salomons</title><title level="j">Zeitschrift für Semitistik und verwandte Gebiete</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Sebastian</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Euringer</t:surname></author><date>1929</date><biblScope unit="volume">7</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">68–85</biblScope><note type="url">http://menadoc.bibliothek.uni-halle.de/dmg/periodical/pageview/98146</note></bibl>).
                </p>
