            <div type="edition">
                <note>This edition of the incipit is based on <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppEt47">UppEt47</ref>. For the incipit,
                    the readings of
                    <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/JXSNIKFS"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Loefgren1962Wandamulette"/><title level="a">Äthiopische Wandamulette</title><title level="j">Orientalia Suecana</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Oscar</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Löfgren</t:surname></author><date>1962</date><biblScope unit="volume">11</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">95-120</biblScope><citedRange unit="page"/></bibl>,
                    whose edition was based on the same manuscript, have been included.</note>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                    <ab>አስማተ፡ <surplus resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ህላሁ፡</surplus> ህላዌሁ<supplied reason="subaudible" resp="JK">፡</supplied> 
                        ለሰሎሞን፡ ንዑድ፡ ኢያስ<supplied reason="subaudible" resp="JK">፡</supplied> ኢያበስ፡ ኢየበአስ፡ አድዳኤል፡
                        ዝቃል፡ ዘወረደ፡ እምሰማይ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ይ<supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ት</supplied>ወለድ፡
                        ክርስቶስ፡ እማርያም፡
                        ኀበ፡ ሀሎ፡ ሰሎሞን፡
                        <app>
                            <lem resp="JK">ሻተክላ<supplied reason="subaudible">፡</supplied></lem>
                            <rdg resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ሸተከላ፡</rdg>
                        </app>
                        <app>
                            <lem resp="JK">ሸተክላ፡</lem>
                            <rdg resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ሸተከላ፡</rdg>
                        </app>
                        <app>
                            <lem resp="JK">ሸተክላ፡</lem>
                            <rdg resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ሸተከላ፡</rdg>
                        </app>
                        ሹኤልሹ፡ 
                        <app>
                            <lem resp="JK">ተሽታሽር፡</lem>
                            <rdg resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ተሸታሸር፡</rdg>
                        </app>
                        ሸላሆም።
                        <app>
                            <lem resp="JK">ሾአቱ፡</lem>
                            <rdg resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ሸአቱ፡</rdg>
                        </app>
                        <app>
                            <lem resp="JK">ሾአቱ፡</lem>
                            <rdg resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ሸአቱ፡</rdg>
                        </app>
                        ዝብልዓቱ<supplied reason="subaudible">፡</supplied>
                        አማኑኤል፡ 
                        <app>
                            <lem resp="JK">ሶመ፡</lem>
                            <rdg resp="PRS6337Lofgren"><unclear>ስመ፡</unclear></rdg>
                        </app>
                        ገቦሁ፡ በዝንቱ፡ አስማቲከ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ 
                        ከመ፡ 
                        <app>
                            <lem resp="JK">እድኃን፡</lem>
                            <rdg resp="PRS6337Lofgren"><unclear>እድኅን፡</unclear></rdg>
                        </app>
                        ሰሎሞን፡ እምእዴሆሙ፡ 
                        ለነሀብት፡ እምድኅረ፡ አኃዝዎ፡ ወአንበርዎ፡ ፫ ዕለተ፡ ወ፫ ሌሊተ<supplied reason="subaudible">፡</supplied>
                        በአምሳለ፡ ንዋም፡ 
                        <app>
                            <lem resp="JK">ወአቀምዎ፡</lem>
                            <rdg resp="PRS6337Lofgren"><surplus>ወ</surplus>አቀምዎ፡</rdg>
                        </app>
                        ቅድመ፡ ንጉሦሙ፡ ለነሀብት፡ ወይቤሎ፡ 
                        አፍራህከኒ፡ ወፈድፋደ፡ ገረምከኒ፡ ምንተ<supplied reason="subaudible" resp="JK">፡</supplied>
                        ረገም<sic resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ገ</sic>ኒ፡ 
                        <app>
                            <lem>ምንተ፡</lem>
                            <rdg resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ምንት፡</rdg>
                        </app>
                        ሀሎ፡ ውስተ፡ ከርሥከ፡ 
                        ወይቤሎ፡ ሰሎሞን፡</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit">
                    <ab>ተማኅፀንኩ፡ ሎፍሐም፡ ዕቀበኒ፡ መዓልተ፡ ወሌሊተ፡ እምሐፅ፡ ዘይሰርር፡ 
                        በመዓልት፡ ወእምግብር፡ ዘየሐውር፡ በጽልመት፡ እምጋኔነ፡ ቀትር።
                    </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
                    <ab>
                        ከመ፡ ይፍታሕ፡ ኵሉ፡ ሥራየ፡ ወኵሉ፡ ዓይነ፡ እኩይ፡ እመሂ። ማሪ፡ ወማሪት፡ ወእመሂ፡ 
